              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "P-SPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Proton spectra were measured at seven angles",
                "ranging from Ang(lab)=5-40 degree.",
                "Alpha spectrum for the Ru-104(d,a)Tc-102 reaction at",
                "Ang(lab)=15-degree was obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "A thin isotopically enriched Mo-100 target, thickness",
                " 100-mug/cm**2, on 10-mug/cm**2 carbon backing was used",
                "for measurement proton spectrum. The energy resolution",
                "to 20 keV FWHM.",
                "A rolled self-supporting metal targets with a",
                "thickness of about 340.0-mug/cm**2 and the isotopically",
                "enrichment more than 96% was used for angular",
                "distribution. The energy resolution of about 40 keV",
                "FWHM.",
                "For the (d,a) experiment, a 100 mug/cm**2 Ru-104 target",
                "was used to measure an alpha spectrum at 15-degree.",
                "A 20 keV FWHM energy resolution was obtained."
              ]
            }
          ],
